title: RUSTY CHANGES Josh Kerr
description: Changes (2008): A series of gigantic tubes -- and not just of the Hawaiian variety -- tempered with innumerable finners and tail-high airs. Stars Jamie O'Brien, Josh Kerr, the Harrington brothers, Jay Davies, Jayke Sharpe and Nate Yeomans. Kerr's section bounces to The Presets' festival anthem Talk Like That, secured, again, well before its commercial release. What are we, freakin' clairvoyants? Not even close. We just like our music served fresh.
